{"article_id":"qi9ldOgZQVDyiM6Y","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"facing harsh criticism from both Republicans and Democrats for his abrupt decisions on Syria ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"claimed a `` breakthrough '' on Wednesday ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"saying","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"the ceasefire on Turkey 's border with Syria was now `` permanent . ''","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Interested in Donald Trump ?","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Add Donald Trump as an interest","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Donald Trump news , video , and analysis from .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Add Interest","depth":3},{"id":9,"text":"`` Early this morning , the Government of Turkey ... said","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that they would be stopping combat and their offensive in Syria ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"making the ceasefire permanent ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and it will indeed be permanent , ''","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Trump said in a formal statement from the White House .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"Trump said","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"sanctions","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"the U.S. imposed on Turkey","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"would be lifted","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"`` unless something happens","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that we 're not happy with . '' `` Today ' s announcement validates our course of action , ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"it had been scorned .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"`` Now , people are saying :","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"'Wow , what a great outcome . ' ''","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"He claimed","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"that the ceasefire is the sole outcome of his administration 's efforts .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Trump 's announcement , though , came a day after Russian President Vladimir Putin and Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan announced","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"they had reached a separate deal for control of northeastern Syria","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"-- where U.S forces have been withdrawn .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"`` This was an outcome","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"created by us , the United States , and nobody else , ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` No other nation , very simple .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"We 're willing to take blame","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"and we 're also willing to take credit . ''","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"\" We have done them a great service","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"and we 've done a great job for all of them , ''","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"speaking of the U.S.-allied Syrian Kurds and Syrian civilians","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"caught in the crossfire .","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"`` And now we 're getting out .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"A long time .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"We were supposed to be there for 30 days .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"That was almost 10 years ago , \"","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"what he said was his promise","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"to get the U.S. out of long-standing wars .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Turkey and Syria have been fighting for centuries ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"adding ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` Let someone else fight over this long-bloodstained sand .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"We 've done a great job","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"and now we 're getting out . ''","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Pres . Trump on withdrawing troops from Syria :","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"`` Let someone else fight over this long bloodstained sand . ''","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"https : //t.co/gIjrUk6LJt","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"pic.twitter.com/ZoZ5W2xWCE - Politics","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"( @ ABCPolitics )","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"October 23 , 2019","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"The president also said","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"he had spoken with the commander of the Syrian Kurdish forces","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Trump claimed","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"\" could not have been more thankful \"","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and that he assured Trump","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that \" ISIS is under very , very strict lock and key ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"and the detention facilities are being strongly maintained . \"","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"The president ' s claim","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that the Syrian Kurds are \" happy \" with the U.S. withdrawal","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"seemed to be contradicted by images of some Kurds","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"throwing rotten vegetables at withdrawing U.S. troops ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Ahmed Omar , the president of the Syrian Democratic Council , said Monday","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that the Kurds have been \" saddened \" by the withdrawal and what he said","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"was the slaughter of his people by Turkish forces :","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"\" They","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"[ Turks ]","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"they want to kill hundreds of thousands of us ...","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"This is why I ask President Trump to stop the attacks ...","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Help us to reach a political solution .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"We want peace .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"We are peaceful people . \"","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Just after touting success on Wednesday , though ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"the president seemed to doubt his own assessment","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"saying permanent is `` questionable '' in that region .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"`` However , you would also define the word permanent","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and that part of the world is somewhat questionable , ''","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Even as Trump made his announcement ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"the top U.S. envoy for Syria , Amb . James Jeffrey , was testifying on Capitol Hill","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"and seemed to contradict the president 's assessment of success .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"`` The Turkish incursion into northeast Syria is a tragedy ,","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"it was long-standing U.S. government policy in two administrations to keep that from happening","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"and we were clearly not successful . ''","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"The president first teased the announcement on Twitter Wednesday morning .","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"In his tweet , the president touted \" big success \" on the Turkish-Syria border ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"heralding","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"that a safe zone has been created","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"and that the ceasefire has held .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` Big success on the Turkey/Syria Border .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Safe Zone created !","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Ceasefire has held","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"and combat missions have ended .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Kurds are safe","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"and have worked very nicely with us .","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Captured ISIS prisoners secured .","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"I will be making a statement at 11:00 A.M. from the White House .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"Thank you ! ''","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Big success on the Turkey/Syria Border .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Safe Zone created !","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Ceasefire has held","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"and combat missions have ended .","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Kurds are safe","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"and have worked very nicely with us .","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"Captured ISIS prisoners secured .","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"I will be making a statement at 11:00 A.M. from the White House .","depth":15},{"id":119,"text":"Thank you !","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"October 23 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"The president 's tweet comes a day after Russian President Vladimir Putin and Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan announced","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"they had reached a separate deal","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"on how to divide up and control northeastern Syria","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"--","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"from which U.S. forces recently withdrew .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"The deal came","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"just before the U.S.-Turkish halt in hostilities reached its deadline ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"with a senior Trump administration official touting it as `` one of the best ceasefires","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"I 've ever seen . ''","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"as the remaining 1,000 U.S. troops withdraw from northeast Syria at President Trump 's command ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"critics have blasted Trump and his administration for ceding this territory to Turkey , Russia and Syrian President Bashar al-Assad ,","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"who has overseen a brutal war against his own people ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"and giving up leverage","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"to accomplish U.S. goals in the region ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"including ensuring the defeat of the Islamic State and expelling Iranian forces from Syria","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"that threaten U.S. allies , especially Israel .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"The deal between Erdogan and Putin calls for Syrian Kurdish forces and their weapons to be removed from a buffer zone the length of the border in northeastern Syria","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"-- an expansive area","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"where these forces live now","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"that extends 30 kilometers","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"( 18.6 miles )","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"in from the border .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"Turkey would maintain control of the portion","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"it now has ,","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"thanks to its agreement with the U.S. ,","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"while Assad 's forces ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"backed by Russia ,","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"would secure the rest of it .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":303,"left":160,"right":302,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":156,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":154,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":159,"left":158,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":5,"right":157,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":177,"right":301,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":164,"right":176,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":164,"left":163,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":9,"right":162,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":162,"left":161,"right":12,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":172,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":170,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"paren